WEBVTT

01:35.930 --> 01:41.289
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.380 --> 01:43.930
[Episode 8]

02:10.800 --> 02:13.440
Mr. Sun, please have a seat.

02:13.630 --> 02:14.280
Thank you.

02:22.370 --> 02:23.460
So,

02:23.840 --> 02:25.870
Yan Zheng was the first human

02:25.890 --> 02:27.850
you treated?

02:30.190 --> 02:30.960
Well...

02:31.950 --> 02:34.470
I couldn't stand aside
and see him die, right?

02:34.470 --> 02:35.810
Actually, I didn't do anything.

02:35.810 --> 02:37.550
He was just lucky.

02:40.100 --> 02:42.550
He was lucky
that he met you when his life was

02:42.590 --> 02:43.720
hanging by a thread.

02:44.220 --> 02:47.020
I'd like to thank you
on Yan Zheng's behalf, Mr. Zhao.

02:47.020 --> 02:47.980
I don't deserve such honor.

02:47.980 --> 02:49.090
I don't deserve it.

02:51.220 --> 02:52.510
Actually, he was

02:52.540 --> 02:56.030
carried back from the wild by my niece.

02:56.060 --> 02:56.870
Otherwise,

02:56.890 --> 02:59.620
he would have frozen to death
in the snow long ago.

03:00.200 --> 03:02.310
So, there is a story behind it.

03:02.330 --> 03:03.050
Indeed.

03:03.080 --> 03:05.850
Otherwise, the couple
wouldn't have gotten married.

03:05.850 --> 03:06.980
Glad to hear that...

03:07.150 --> 03:07.840
Married?

03:08.760 --> 03:09.890
You mean Jiuheng...

03:10.840 --> 03:12.000
Well, no.

03:12.200 --> 03:13.230
You mean Yan Zheng

03:13.260 --> 03:14.740
got married?

03:14.800 --> 03:17.230
No, technically,
he's a matrilocal husband.

03:17.230 --> 03:19.620
Zheng married into our family.

03:20.150 --> 03:21.610
Married into your family?

03:23.820 --> 03:26.680
Xie Jiuheng actually became
a matrilocal husband?

03:27.220 --> 03:29.160
Who in the world would dare
make him do that?

03:29.160 --> 03:31.720
Even the Emperor wouldn't dare make him
a matrilocal husband.

03:31.720 --> 03:33.460
He was badly injured back then

03:33.480 --> 03:34.820
and couldn't even get out of bed.

03:34.820 --> 03:37.680
It was Changyu who butchered pigs
to earn money

03:37.700 --> 03:39.570
and buy him medicine for treatment.

03:39.570 --> 03:42.430
She saved his life.

03:43.960 --> 03:47.510
Mrs. Fan is a butcher?

03:47.910 --> 03:49.930
My sister is amazing.

03:50.060 --> 03:52.890
She can knock a pig out
with a single slap.

03:54.730 --> 03:55.870
Let go of me!

03:58.600 --> 04:00.120
I'll ask you one last time.

04:00.770 --> 04:02.400
Will you marry into my family or not?

04:02.400 --> 04:03.220
Let go!

04:06.660 --> 04:07.810
If you refuse,

04:08.690 --> 04:10.140
you'll end up like this.

04:13.020 --> 04:14.900
I'd rather die
than marry into your family!

04:14.900 --> 04:15.960
Let go of me!

04:15.980 --> 04:19.459
Even if you die, you belong to my family!

04:24.930 --> 04:28.590
So Yan Zheng marrying into her family was
taking on a challenge...

04:28.610 --> 04:30.780
No, I mean he was repaying kindness.

04:31.280 --> 04:33.409
It wasn't entirely to repay kindness.

04:34.030 --> 04:36.640
The couple is deeply in love.

04:36.860 --> 04:39.950
When Changyu was bullied
by that ingrate Song Yan,

04:40.110 --> 04:42.540
Yan Zheng stood up for her.

04:43.030 --> 04:43.760
Also,

04:44.020 --> 04:47.010
when her uncle tried to seize
her inheritance and house,

04:47.010 --> 04:49.280
it was Yan Zheng who helped out.

04:49.790 --> 04:51.620
My sister's hands got chapped
from working.

04:51.620 --> 04:52.980
Zheng felt bad

04:53.000 --> 04:55.320
and bought her balm.

04:56.520 --> 04:59.080
Are you talking about the same person?

04:59.600 --> 05:02.750
Did your niece damage Yan Zheng's brain?

05:02.830 --> 05:03.340
Yes...

05:04.250 --> 05:05.650
No, no.

05:05.780 --> 05:07.180
His brain isn't damaged.

05:09.180 --> 05:10.690
When Yan Zheng recovers,

05:10.720 --> 05:12.480
he won't need to work
as an escort anymore.

05:12.480 --> 05:14.280
The couple can run the pork stall

05:14.300 --> 05:16.730
and have endless pork for life.

05:18.670 --> 05:26.820
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

05:24.150 --> 05:25.230
Wipe my sweat!

05:36.960 --> 05:40.100
Mr. Sun, you saved my niece's husband.

05:40.460 --> 05:41.970
Changyu will be back soon,

05:42.000 --> 05:43.580
and she'll definitely
repay you generously.

05:43.580 --> 05:45.220
Changyu is an honest person.

05:45.450 --> 05:47.120
If you show her a little kindness,

05:47.120 --> 05:48.870
she'll return it tenfold.

05:49.290 --> 05:51.159
Benefactor, Chang Yu will surely repay

05:51.159 --> 05:53.620
your great kindness today
when she returns.

05:53.630 --> 05:54.390
Benefactor!

05:58.480 --> 05:59.750
Benefactor!

06:05.630 --> 06:07.760
So you're the one who saved my husband.

06:12.780 --> 06:14.410
This pig is for you!

06:18.350 --> 06:19.160
Here you are!

06:22.020 --> 06:22.940
Sir.

06:23.690 --> 06:24.910
-Mr. Sun?
-Mr. Sun.

06:25.900 --> 06:27.500
-Benefactor!
-Benefactor!

06:29.690 --> 06:31.710
Is something wrong?

06:32.470 --> 06:34.680
No, nothing.

06:35.390 --> 06:36.480
Yan Zheng!

06:37.950 --> 06:39.270
Changyu is back!

06:46.510 --> 06:47.840
Welcome back, Changyu.

06:48.380 --> 06:49.350
-Changyu.
-Uncle.

06:49.350 --> 06:51.210
This is Benefactor Sun,
whom I mentioned to you on the way.

06:51.210 --> 06:51.810
Yes, yes.

06:51.920 --> 06:53.310
This is the benefactor.

06:54.980 --> 06:56.350
I-I'm flattered.

07:00.520 --> 07:01.730
By the way, Mr. Zhao.

07:02.210 --> 07:03.360
I have a prescription here.

07:03.360 --> 07:04.870
It can help Yan Zheng fully recover.

07:04.870 --> 07:06.460
That's wonderful.

07:06.520 --> 07:08.190
I'll go to town right now
to get the medicine.

07:08.190 --> 07:08.800
Let's go quickly.

07:08.800 --> 07:11.000
Changyu, we're off to get the medicine.

07:12.860 --> 07:14.310
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

07:14.580 --> 07:16.500
I should be the one
thanking you, Mrs. Fan.

07:16.500 --> 07:19.030
Thank you
for taking care of him all this time.

07:29.200 --> 07:30.840
Why hasn't he woken up yet?

07:31.040 --> 07:32.630
Is he in a coma?

07:32.830 --> 07:33.500
It's fine.

07:33.870 --> 07:34.920
He took the Nine-turn Pill.

07:34.920 --> 07:36.120
It's normal for him to sleep for a while.

07:36.120 --> 07:37.180
He'll wake up soon.

07:41.720 --> 07:42.780
Please take a seat.

07:45.409 --> 07:46.480
Have some tea, please.

07:46.480 --> 07:47.110
Thank you.

07:56.590 --> 07:57.930
Are you his master?

07:59.080 --> 08:01.010
Yan Zheng has no master.

08:01.910 --> 08:04.870
No one in this world would dare
to be his master.

08:08.380 --> 08:10.040
Then you're his close friend?

08:12.330 --> 08:14.310
Before I came, I thought I was.

08:14.390 --> 08:15.600
But now that I'm here,

08:16.200 --> 08:17.360
I found out that this man
didn't even tell me

08:17.360 --> 08:19.820
about something as important
as getting married.

08:19.820 --> 08:21.750
So I'm not sure anymore.

08:22.070 --> 08:23.330
It happened suddenly.

08:23.740 --> 08:25.450
It's not entirely his fault.

08:27.890 --> 08:29.620
I begged him.

08:31.920 --> 08:33.559
You begged him to be
your matrilocal husband,

08:33.559 --> 08:34.580
and he agreed?

08:36.630 --> 08:37.580
Sort of.

08:39.840 --> 08:41.440
It turns out all those noble ladies
in the capital

08:41.440 --> 08:43.370
lost because they didn't speak up.

08:44.039 --> 08:47.210
[Xigu Lane]

08:58.310 --> 09:00.020
What exactly happened recently?

09:00.020 --> 09:02.540
How did you end up
with that female butcher?

09:04.030 --> 09:05.410
I was secretly investigating

09:05.410 --> 09:07.340
the Jinzhou case from 16 years ago.

09:07.730 --> 09:09.790
But on the battlefield in Chongzhou,

09:10.440 --> 09:11.970
I was shot by a hidden arrow.

09:24.810 --> 09:26.170
Xie Yi and Xie San

09:27.290 --> 09:29.950
desperately fought their way
out of the ambush,

09:30.600 --> 09:33.200
but ended up being hacked to death
by the enemy.

10:41.750 --> 10:44.120
I drifted down the river to Jizhou.

10:56.560 --> 10:58.490
In the end, I collapsed in the snow.

10:59.610 --> 11:00.760
She saved me.

11:02.720 --> 11:04.470
Who on earth wanted you dead?

11:05.770 --> 11:07.300
There's no solid proof yet,

11:08.250 --> 11:09.920
but I have a pretty good guess.

11:10.790 --> 11:12.920
Should we contact your uncle for help?

11:22.670 --> 11:24.120
No way.

11:24.390 --> 11:25.660
Was it...

11:25.800 --> 11:28.460
Was it Prime Minister Wei
who wanted to kill you?

11:28.520 --> 11:30.240
He raised you from childhood

11:30.270 --> 11:31.760
and found the best teachers
to educate you.

11:31.760 --> 11:32.440
Why...

11:38.140 --> 11:40.740
What reason would he possibly have
to kill you?

11:41.490 --> 11:42.940
I want to know, too.

11:44.870 --> 11:46.030
Right when I happened to be investigating

11:46.030 --> 11:47.960
the Jinzhou case from 16 years ago,

11:49.030 --> 11:51.030
he just couldn't wait to make a move.

11:51.980 --> 11:54.300
I found this the day
the Fan's house was attacked.

11:54.300 --> 11:55.910
The Wei family's Iron Suicide Warriors.

11:55.910 --> 11:57.440
Seventeen of them in total.

11:58.710 --> 12:00.200
I've heard that the Wei family has

12:00.200 --> 12:02.590
four ranks of Suicide Warriors—
Heaven, Earth, Dark, and Yellow.

12:02.590 --> 12:04.000
If he wanted to kill you,

12:04.270 --> 12:05.600
sending only
a few Dark-rank Suicide Warriors

12:05.600 --> 12:06.730
would not be enough.

12:07.080 --> 12:08.670
Then they came for Mrs. Fan?

12:09.830 --> 12:11.360
That makes even less sense.

12:11.610 --> 12:13.910
Mrs. Fan's family are
just ordinary people.

12:13.910 --> 12:16.390
How could they have grudges
against the Prime Minister?

12:16.390 --> 12:17.670
It is indeed fishy.

12:18.470 --> 12:20.270
They ransacked the Fan's house,

12:20.510 --> 12:23.510
seemingly looking for something.

12:25.310 --> 12:26.770
Looking for something?

12:27.370 --> 12:28.440
The Fan's house...

12:29.640 --> 12:31.030
All these unsolved cases are

12:31.030 --> 12:32.890
tangled like a messy ball of yarn.

12:34.250 --> 12:35.360
But you found the thread

12:35.360 --> 12:37.090
immediately

12:37.120 --> 12:39.380
and traced it directly to the Fan family.

12:39.610 --> 12:41.320
As expected of you, Xie Jiuheng.

12:41.320 --> 12:43.230
I didn't find the thread.

12:44.910 --> 12:46.510
She just happened to save me.

13:12.970 --> 13:14.100
No, don't look back.

13:21.040 --> 13:21.940
Done.

13:22.390 --> 13:24.030
Hello, Mr. Sun.

13:24.160 --> 13:24.970
Hello.

13:26.780 --> 13:28.030
Changning, you just look

13:28.030 --> 13:29.760
like a kind and sensible child,

13:30.320 --> 13:31.320
feeding the rabbits

13:31.320 --> 13:32.380
and the chicken...

13:35.300 --> 13:36.430
Gyrfalcon?

13:38.170 --> 13:40.900
Mr. Sun, you saved
my sister and brother-in-law.

13:41.420 --> 13:42.750
You are our benefactor.

13:43.160 --> 13:44.950
The falcon saved me.

13:45.080 --> 13:47.220
So it is a benefactor bird.

13:47.250 --> 13:49.660
So the rabbits need to grow up quickly.

13:49.750 --> 13:52.750
Then the falcon can eat them later.

14:04.200 --> 14:05.810
Your brother-in-law saved you, too.

14:05.810 --> 14:06.970
How will you repay him?

14:06.970 --> 14:09.680
When Zheng and Changyu have a baby,

14:09.750 --> 14:11.950
I'll teach the baby how to butcher pigs.

14:12.480 --> 14:14.550
Changning, stop playing with the rabbits.

14:14.550 --> 14:16.410
Remember to wash the vegetables.

14:17.670 --> 14:18.670
Mr. Sun?

14:19.110 --> 14:19.770
Let me do it.

14:20.620 --> 14:22.530
We can't have a guest do chores.

14:22.550 --> 14:23.430
It's fine!

14:23.460 --> 14:25.120
I can't eat your food for free.

14:25.950 --> 14:26.950
Thank you, then.

14:27.050 --> 14:27.710
No problem.

14:30.150 --> 14:32.970
I have to make Yan Zheng owe me this one.

14:33.040 --> 14:34.530
When we get back to Luyuan,

14:34.560 --> 14:36.560
I'll make him repay me for this meal.

14:41.470 --> 14:43.600
Yan Zheng is also going back to Luyuan?

14:46.980 --> 14:47.700
He...

14:48.940 --> 14:51.070
He still has many unfulfilled wishes.

14:51.190 --> 14:53.320
He will definitely leave afterwards.

14:53.730 --> 14:54.470
Didn't he

14:54.920 --> 14:56.230
tell you?

14:56.580 --> 14:57.760
After I recover,

14:58.330 --> 14:59.610
I will leave.

15:00.610 --> 15:02.210
I won't overstay my welcome.

15:05.270 --> 15:06.080
He did.

15:07.040 --> 15:08.100
He did tell me that.

15:10.050 --> 15:10.800
That's good.

15:37.750 --> 15:38.410
Did you

15:38.730 --> 15:40.790
really fall for that female butcher?

15:43.680 --> 15:44.440
Alright, alright.

15:44.440 --> 15:45.630
I'll stop asking.

15:47.910 --> 15:50.570
You were still acting tough
in court yesterday.

15:50.590 --> 15:52.120
If I hadn't arrived in time,

15:52.250 --> 15:55.110
you'd have been totally screwed
by now, I'm afraid.

15:55.180 --> 15:56.780
It was all for her, wasn't it?

16:05.650 --> 16:07.160
In my current situation,

16:08.010 --> 16:10.270
with my national
and family vengeance unresolved,

16:10.270 --> 16:12.110
and with my serious injuries
still unhealed,

16:12.110 --> 16:15.110
falling for someone
would only bring them disasters.

16:15.770 --> 16:16.720
If you were me,

16:18.690 --> 16:20.890
would you let yourself fall in love now?

16:25.440 --> 16:26.360
Humans are

16:27.730 --> 16:30.330
not deities
who cut off emotions and desires.

16:31.510 --> 16:32.670
It's hard to control

16:34.720 --> 16:35.940
your feelings.

16:42.250 --> 16:43.650
You should go back early.

16:43.930 --> 16:46.210
Secretly investigate
Wei Yan's movements for me.

16:46.210 --> 16:49.100
The situation on the battlefield is
shifting rapidly.

16:49.100 --> 16:52.160
With that coward Wei Xuan
commanding the Three Armies,

16:52.600 --> 16:55.190
the situation in the Northwest will surely
undergo drastic changes.

16:55.190 --> 16:56.990
The time I can hide my identity is

16:57.530 --> 16:58.260
running out.

16:59.120 --> 17:01.360
Prince Changxin will definitely
march south.

17:01.360 --> 17:02.360
And Old General He

17:03.150 --> 17:05.200
will surely be unable to hold out alone.

17:05.200 --> 17:08.130
Why don't you leave with me tomorrow,
Your Lordship?

17:32.270 --> 17:33.130
Changyu,

17:33.200 --> 17:35.720
the government has already
closed your family's case.

17:34.340 --> 17:39.490
[Qingping County Government Office]

17:37.920 --> 17:38.550
Mr. Wang,

17:38.720 --> 17:40.240
we haven't found the mastermind yet.

17:40.240 --> 17:42.500
How could they close the case so hastily?

17:42.860 --> 17:44.160
The people who died
in the pine forest were

17:44.160 --> 17:45.030
the culprits.

17:45.810 --> 17:48.510
They were bandits
from the Qingfeng Stronghold.

17:48.510 --> 17:49.980
How could it be bandits?

17:51.320 --> 17:53.280
Why would bandits ransack my home?

17:53.790 --> 17:54.980
I was thinking,

17:55.000 --> 17:57.920
perhaps when your father worked
as an escort years ago,

17:57.920 --> 17:59.370
he offended someone.

18:00.690 --> 18:02.350
Changyu, listen to my advice.

18:02.530 --> 18:05.040
Sell your pigsty, house, and land,

18:05.520 --> 18:07.650
and go hide somewhere else for a while.

18:09.900 --> 18:11.060
Father, Mother.

18:12.870 --> 18:14.000
Tell me,

18:14.240 --> 18:15.900
should I take Changning away?

18:18.070 --> 18:19.190
Do you think

18:19.240 --> 18:20.830
Yan Zheng will go with me?

18:24.850 --> 18:27.380
I'm afraid I've got him
caught up in this mess.

18:33.400 --> 18:34.160
Changyu.

18:34.850 --> 18:36.580
Why are you sitting here alone?

18:37.200 --> 18:38.220
What's wrong, Mrs. Wang?

18:38.220 --> 18:40.280
Did a rich relative visit your place?

18:40.360 --> 18:40.990
Why?

18:41.030 --> 18:42.000
I just saw the carriage

18:42.000 --> 18:43.550
that left your house.

18:43.550 --> 18:46.810
It was even grander
than the Song family's when they moved.

18:50.800 --> 18:52.490
The basket! Your basket!

19:40.960 --> 19:42.630
[Fill Your Belly]

19:45.920 --> 19:46.590
[Today, I'm bidding a farewell
to you, Mrs. Fan.]

19:46.350 --> 19:47.030
Today...

19:46.620 --> 19:47.380
[Wish you a peaceful life,
year after year. Best regards.]

19:47.790 --> 19:48.680
Bid...

19:49.320 --> 19:50.950
A farewell to you, Mrs. Fan.

19:51.710 --> 19:53.110
Wish you a peaceful life.

20:10.200 --> 20:11.350
Changyu.

20:12.750 --> 20:13.870
Did Zheng leave?

20:18.840 --> 20:20.240
It's good that he's gone.

20:21.130 --> 20:21.960
That's good.

20:23.030 --> 20:25.000
If there's any more trouble in the future,

20:25.000 --> 20:26.530
he won't be dragged into it.

20:29.810 --> 20:31.350
Why didn't he say goodbye?

20:36.330 --> 20:38.000
Zheng is back.

20:54.680 --> 20:55.770
Yan Zheng, you...

20:58.000 --> 21:00.340
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

21:00.720 --> 21:04.180
Zheng went to Mrs. Zhuang's place
to read a letter for the old lady.

21:01.270 --> 21:02.600
♪ With very pale colors ♪

21:03.510 --> 21:06.340
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

21:05.990 --> 21:07.270
She has trouble walking,

21:06.690 --> 21:09.270
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

21:07.300 --> 21:09.830
so I went over there
to read the letter for her.

21:09.930 --> 21:11.570
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

21:12.090 --> 21:16.390
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

21:13.200 --> 21:14.000
What's wrong?

21:14.720 --> 21:15.580
Are you crying?

21:18.110 --> 21:19.350
No way.

21:19.780 --> 21:22.180
The smoke from the cured meat
got in my eyes.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.640
Sun has left.

21:26.920 --> 21:28.110
He left some money.

21:32.270 --> 21:35.070
Mr. Sun likes things tidy.

21:35.160 --> 21:36.030
Before he left,

21:36.030 --> 21:38.550
he cleaned the house thoroughly.

21:45.510 --> 21:47.720
I came to look for straw ropes

21:47.740 --> 21:49.000
to hang the cured meat.

22:12.050 --> 22:13.250
Why did I take a chain?

22:17.720 --> 22:18.810
To make cured meat,

22:18.880 --> 22:21.000
you need to salt it for 7 to 8 days,

22:21.000 --> 22:22.750
and then smoke it with cypress branches.

22:22.750 --> 22:24.790
That way, the meat lasts longer.

22:24.910 --> 22:25.560
Look,

22:26.240 --> 22:28.000
the meat I smoked a few days ago is

22:28.000 --> 22:29.400
ready to eat now.

22:29.510 --> 22:31.720
I'll send some to Grandfather tomorrow.

22:31.720 --> 22:34.650
The medicine is on the table.
Drink it while it's hot.

22:34.880 --> 22:35.470
Okay.

22:38.810 --> 22:40.720
I went to the magistrate's office today.

22:40.720 --> 22:42.750
Mr. Wang said the case is closed.

22:43.830 --> 22:45.000
But we still

22:45.160 --> 22:47.440
don't know if those people were

22:47.550 --> 22:49.160
after money or revenge.

22:52.030 --> 22:53.550
If it's for revenge,

22:54.270 --> 22:56.400
they will definitely come back again.

22:57.250 --> 22:58.450
What do you plan to do?

22:59.880 --> 23:02.920
I plan to sell the property
after the festival

23:03.480 --> 23:05.880
and take Changning away
to hide for a while.

23:08.310 --> 23:10.640
If you're leaving, the sooner the better.

23:11.720 --> 23:13.360
But it's almost New Year,

23:13.440 --> 23:14.900
and it's snowing outside.

23:15.720 --> 23:17.350
The paperwork for selling the property

23:17.350 --> 23:19.150
will take some time to transfer.

23:19.440 --> 23:20.590
In a few days,

23:20.720 --> 23:22.780
your injury will also heal a bit more.

23:22.830 --> 23:23.830
What do you think?

23:26.510 --> 23:27.160
Me?

23:28.880 --> 23:31.150
Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao are
really nice people.

23:31.150 --> 23:34.110
Their son died outside in the war.

23:34.270 --> 23:36.730
I want to leave my fields
to them for farming.

23:37.020 --> 23:39.950
Also, I'll write the divorce paper
for you in advance

23:40.190 --> 23:42.720
and leave you some money
for travel expenses.

23:44.960 --> 23:46.160
I have my own plans.

23:47.190 --> 23:48.990
You don't need to worry about me.

23:49.820 --> 23:51.430
Then will you go with me?

23:56.130 --> 23:58.890
Or do you want to stay here to heal?

24:02.550 --> 24:03.480
I'll go with you.

24:08.310 --> 24:10.370
Then help me hang the cured meat, too.

24:30.050 --> 24:31.360
Did your parents leave
any inheritance behind

24:31.360 --> 24:33.600
that you want to take with you?

24:37.160 --> 24:37.830
Yes.

24:41.070 --> 24:42.130
My butcher knives.

24:42.310 --> 24:44.670
I take that set with me wherever I go.

24:44.860 --> 24:47.190
With them,
I can butcher pigs for a living.

24:47.510 --> 24:49.440
If we run into hooligans on the way,

24:49.480 --> 24:51.100
I can also use them to defend us.

24:51.100 --> 24:51.960
Anything else?

24:53.770 --> 24:54.630
The title deed!

24:55.400 --> 24:57.020
Since the case is closed,

24:57.270 --> 24:58.800
I'll take it out in a moment.

24:59.450 --> 25:00.450
The title deed...

25:01.710 --> 25:03.910
Did your parents ever mention anything

25:04.310 --> 25:05.350
that you must take with you,

25:05.350 --> 25:07.590
even if you're running for your life?

25:10.920 --> 25:11.510
Yes.

25:11.550 --> 25:12.200
What is it?

25:12.750 --> 25:13.400
My sister.

25:22.640 --> 25:23.480
Darn it...

25:28.270 --> 25:29.110
Tangerine peel candy.

25:29.110 --> 25:30.110
I've tasted it.

25:30.110 --> 25:33.110
It's sweet and sour,
and it helps with the bitterness.

25:33.900 --> 25:34.580
Thank you.

25:44.440 --> 25:46.440
That girl is a real jinx.

25:47.920 --> 25:49.840
She not only brought about
her parents' deaths

25:49.840 --> 25:51.850
but also implicated her uncle.

25:51.650 --> 25:54.180
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Daniu]

25:51.980 --> 25:54.080
How did Fan Daniu

25:54.240 --> 25:56.270
end up being killed by bandits?

25:57.070 --> 25:58.110
Maybe

25:58.130 --> 26:00.920
Fan Changyu paid someone to kill him.

26:00.950 --> 26:02.700
Shut up, Granny Kang.

26:03.110 --> 26:05.310
Save some karma for your two grandsons.

26:05.430 --> 26:07.560
What? Your eldest son died,

26:07.590 --> 26:09.020
and your daughter-in-law
ran off with someone.

26:09.020 --> 26:11.090
Are you also a jinx,
having caused all these?

26:11.090 --> 26:12.900
You... You're full of crap!

26:15.440 --> 26:15.970
Changyu.

26:17.190 --> 26:18.120
Changyu is here.

26:20.960 --> 26:22.550
Fan Changyu!

26:23.790 --> 26:25.160
Fan Changyu,

26:25.590 --> 26:27.320
how dare you show up here again?

26:28.960 --> 26:31.450
You brat! I'm going to beat you to death!

26:36.790 --> 26:37.550
How could Changyu

26:37.550 --> 26:38.270
fight her?

26:38.270 --> 26:39.470
She's way out of line!

26:40.030 --> 26:40.590
Changyu.

26:40.590 --> 26:41.950
You jinx!

26:42.070 --> 26:42.480
I'm fine.

26:42.480 --> 26:44.200
Getting Fan Daniu killed wasn't enough,

26:44.200 --> 26:45.590
and now you dare come to my house?

26:45.590 --> 26:47.300
I'll teach you a lesson!

26:49.440 --> 26:50.070
I came

26:50.680 --> 26:52.680
to bring something to Grandfather.

26:53.110 --> 26:54.840
I'm not here to stir up trouble.

26:55.030 --> 26:56.430
If you go past this blade,

26:57.160 --> 26:58.960
I'll cut out your filthy tongue.

27:00.790 --> 27:01.850
What does she mean?

27:01.920 --> 27:03.050
She's too arrogant.

27:04.080 --> 27:04.880
Grandfather.

27:05.950 --> 27:07.610
I brought you some cured meat.

27:07.680 --> 27:08.880
Oh, Changyu.

27:13.000 --> 27:14.130
How are you feeling?

27:15.640 --> 27:16.970
Had anyone bullied you?

27:17.000 --> 27:17.880
No.

27:18.400 --> 27:19.720
No one bullies me.

27:20.830 --> 27:21.750
Changyu,

27:22.790 --> 27:25.590
Daniu and Erniu are both gone.

27:27.100 --> 27:28.340
There is something

27:28.960 --> 27:31.190
I can't take to my grave.

27:32.070 --> 27:35.440
-In fact, your father is my...
-It was her father,

27:35.440 --> 27:36.550
Fan Erniu!

27:37.090 --> 27:38.510
Ever since they came home,

27:38.510 --> 27:40.460
we haven't had a single good day.

27:40.590 --> 27:44.020
My Daniu was cursed to death
because of their family.

27:45.400 --> 27:47.120
Sooner or later, our whole family

27:47.120 --> 27:49.060
will die because of her!

27:51.720 --> 27:53.950
Grandfather, take care of yourself.

27:53.980 --> 27:55.110
I'm taking my leave.

27:55.280 --> 27:56.810
I'll visit you another day.

28:10.510 --> 28:11.910
Look at her! Look!

28:11.960 --> 28:12.900
This girl.

28:13.070 --> 28:15.800
She doesn't even
pay respects to her uncle!

28:18.630 --> 28:20.970
It's karma...

28:26.950 --> 28:29.410
[South Market]

28:29.530 --> 28:31.910
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

28:31.910 --> 28:38.290
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

28:36.920 --> 28:37.640
Changyu.

28:39.550 --> 28:40.990
Closing up so early?

28:41.680 --> 28:43.940
Mr. Li, I'm not doing business today.

28:43.960 --> 28:45.370
Not even with me?

28:47.000 --> 28:48.600
Something happened at home.

28:49.680 --> 28:52.700
I don't plan to open the shop
until the end of the year.

28:52.790 --> 28:54.580
I'm not here to buy meat today.

28:54.790 --> 28:56.450
Our manager wants to see you.

28:57.980 --> 29:02.160
[Yixiang Restaurant]

28:58.520 --> 28:59.580
Sir,

28:59.920 --> 29:00.830
welcome.

29:03.570 --> 29:04.660
You're back.

29:06.750 --> 29:07.790
Take care, sir and madam.

29:07.790 --> 29:09.410
Changyu, look.

29:09.680 --> 29:12.340
This is the main hall
of our Yixiang Restaurant.

29:12.400 --> 29:13.230
Take a look.

29:13.250 --> 29:14.450
It's so magnificent.

29:14.910 --> 29:15.740
Of course.

29:16.410 --> 29:18.590
It's the best in Lin'an.

29:19.710 --> 29:21.080
It's actually not busy right now.

29:21.080 --> 29:22.370
During festivals,

29:22.450 --> 29:24.370
it's so crowded
that there's almost nowhere to stand.

29:24.370 --> 29:25.370
It's so bustling!

29:27.880 --> 29:28.680
Welcome back.

29:30.920 --> 29:32.100
It's huge.

29:32.310 --> 29:34.370
Come on, Changyu. It's just up ahead.

29:36.000 --> 29:37.160
I'll leave you here.

29:37.310 --> 29:38.260
The manager is inside.

29:38.260 --> 29:39.220
Go on in.

30:19.970 --> 30:22.100
Manager, Mrs. Fan is here.

30:25.480 --> 30:26.950
Changyu, is it you?

30:42.540 --> 30:46.130
So you are the manager
of Yixiang Restaurant.

30:46.440 --> 30:47.770
I always thought

30:48.270 --> 30:50.450
the manager here was a man.

30:51.960 --> 30:53.500
Before I met you,

30:53.520 --> 30:54.200
I also never thought

30:54.200 --> 30:55.590
a lady who butchers pigs

30:55.610 --> 30:57.090
would be so beautiful.

30:58.140 --> 31:00.180
You are the beautiful one.

31:02.230 --> 31:04.050
My surname is Yu,
and my given name is Qianqian.

31:04.050 --> 31:05.710
I'm a few years older than you,

31:06.270 --> 31:09.300
so I'll take the liberty
of calling you Changyu.

31:09.440 --> 31:10.940
I heard from Mr. Li

31:11.200 --> 31:12.680
that you can not only butcher pigs,

31:12.680 --> 31:15.280
but also make
really delectable braised meat.

31:15.330 --> 31:17.210
Thank you for the compliment, Manager.

31:17.210 --> 31:18.990
Don't be modest.

31:19.510 --> 31:20.870
I saw

31:20.900 --> 31:24.030
you smash the signboard
of the Wang's Braised Meat Shop.

31:26.050 --> 31:27.770
I did smash it,

31:28.330 --> 31:29.910
but I didn't start it.

31:30.310 --> 31:32.030
It doesn't matter who started it.

31:32.030 --> 31:34.160
You were right to smash their signboard.

31:34.160 --> 31:35.960
Ever since the Young Master of the Wang's

31:35.960 --> 31:37.830
took over the Wang's Braised Meat Shop,

31:37.830 --> 31:38.960
he's been dishonest in business

31:38.960 --> 31:40.270
and handsy during interactions.

31:40.270 --> 31:43.000
I've long wanted
to end my partnership with them.

31:44.920 --> 31:45.850
Bring it up here.

31:48.830 --> 31:49.720
Bring it in.

31:54.920 --> 31:56.070
To be honest with you,

31:56.070 --> 31:58.670
I had someone buy your braised meat
for 10 days.

31:59.030 --> 31:59.880
The consistent quality

31:59.880 --> 32:01.080
and the same portions

32:01.200 --> 32:03.600
proved that you truly are
an honest person.

32:03.680 --> 32:05.550
That's how we're supposed to do business.

32:05.550 --> 32:06.550
My father said,

32:06.630 --> 32:08.830
"Dishonest business won't last long."

32:08.920 --> 32:12.590
So, regarding the braised meat business,

32:13.720 --> 32:14.980
I want to work with you.

32:17.550 --> 32:19.860
Thank you for your appreciation, Manager.

32:19.860 --> 32:22.490
But I can't make this deal with you.

32:23.030 --> 32:23.790
Why?

32:24.200 --> 32:26.060
Something happened in my family.

32:26.170 --> 32:28.500
I'll be leaving Lin'an after the New Year.

32:31.960 --> 32:33.230
In this case,

32:33.550 --> 32:36.030
the town will lose your delicious dishes.

32:39.550 --> 32:41.280
If you really like it, Manager,

32:41.790 --> 32:44.450
I can tell you the ingredients
and how to make it.

32:45.320 --> 32:48.450
You can just have your staff
make it following my recipe.

32:53.790 --> 32:55.820
You are such a straightforward girl!

32:55.820 --> 32:57.070
I've only chatted with you for a bit,

32:57.070 --> 32:59.590
and you've already
given your secret recipe away.

32:59.590 --> 33:00.830
If you go somewhere far from home,

33:00.830 --> 33:02.690
you must keep your wits about you.

33:03.790 --> 33:06.390
Mr. Li and my father
had been friends for years.

33:07.070 --> 33:08.470
When my father was alive,

33:08.780 --> 33:11.160
he often supported
our butcher shop's business.

33:11.160 --> 33:12.160
I thought,

33:12.920 --> 33:14.510
since Mr. Li is so nice,

33:14.970 --> 33:17.910
his manager must be
a wonderful person, too.

33:20.550 --> 33:21.790
Giving you the recipe

33:22.400 --> 33:24.310
will allow the people of Lin'an Town

33:24.310 --> 33:26.460
to taste the cooking
my parents left behind.

33:26.460 --> 33:28.930
They'd surely be happy about it in heaven.

33:38.560 --> 33:39.480
Come with me.

33:45.590 --> 33:46.270
Look.

33:47.000 --> 33:48.070
During the New Year,

33:48.070 --> 33:49.400
my business is booming.

33:49.750 --> 33:51.400
The banquets are fully booked.

33:51.400 --> 33:54.130
So the demand for braised meat is
naturally high.

33:54.240 --> 33:56.620
Those old gourmets are very picky diners.

33:56.750 --> 33:57.640
How about this?

33:57.920 --> 34:00.960
You supply the braised meat to us
for the New Year first,

34:00.960 --> 34:04.270
and I'll figure out a way to fill the gap
after the New Year.

34:05.790 --> 34:07.610
You'll need to buy a new house
in a new place.

34:07.610 --> 34:09.340
That will cost a bunch of money.

34:09.670 --> 34:10.900
I'll pay you extra.

34:10.980 --> 34:13.980
Just help me get through
this end of the year smoothly.

34:15.810 --> 34:17.940
This is indeed a good way to make money.

34:19.810 --> 34:21.730
Thank you, Manager Yu.

34:22.320 --> 34:24.120
I should be the one thanking you.

34:24.630 --> 34:26.070
For the Wang's braised meat,

34:26.070 --> 34:27.400
we used to buy it

34:27.440 --> 34:29.239
at 40 wen a catty
regardless of the season.

34:29.239 --> 34:30.340
With today's high meat prices

34:30.340 --> 34:31.940
and your excellent quality,

34:32.090 --> 34:34.679
I'll give you 50 wen.

34:35.040 --> 34:36.760
From now on, you'll make braised meat
in the kitchen.

34:36.760 --> 34:38.159
Wages will be paid daily.

34:38.800 --> 34:39.920
That's too much.

34:39.920 --> 34:40.800
It's not.

34:41.400 --> 34:42.670
Generous in friendship,

34:42.670 --> 34:43.929
exacting in business.

34:44.360 --> 34:45.340
Tomorrow,

34:45.360 --> 34:47.889
come over,
and I'll draw up a contract for you.

34:48.110 --> 34:49.630
To show my sincerity,

34:49.800 --> 34:51.190
I'm willing to pay a deposit first.

34:51.190 --> 34:51.830
Fuling.

34:55.360 --> 34:56.760
T-This won't do.

34:56.880 --> 34:57.920
We haven't signed the contract,

34:57.920 --> 34:59.320
and if I take your money now,

34:59.320 --> 35:00.640
it wouldn't be right.

35:01.070 --> 35:03.200
I'm afraid you'll go back on your word.

35:03.640 --> 35:04.820
Just take it.

35:05.800 --> 35:06.630
If you don't take it,

35:06.630 --> 35:08.090
I won't feel at ease.

35:14.510 --> 35:15.980
Then I accept.

35:16.410 --> 35:17.670
Thank you, Manager Yu.

35:18.670 --> 35:21.130
I'm happy today. So don't call me Manager.

35:21.890 --> 35:22.730
Call me

35:23.810 --> 35:24.690
Qianqian.

35:27.480 --> 35:28.680
Thank you, Qianqian.

35:36.180 --> 35:39.570
Manager! Come out!

35:39.600 --> 35:41.400
Stop playing the pipa!

35:41.990 --> 35:44.440
Chef Li, come out right now!

35:44.460 --> 35:46.580
Guo, what are you doing?

35:46.610 --> 35:47.780
What do you mean?

35:47.810 --> 35:50.220
We only cooperated
because the Fan family had an incident.

35:50.220 --> 35:51.980
Now it's the agreed date.

35:52.030 --> 35:53.110
Don't you know that?

35:53.110 --> 35:55.160
Bullshit!

35:56.150 --> 35:58.150
When you were short of meat,
you came to me for help.

35:58.150 --> 35:59.760
Now the little brat from the Fan family is

35:59.760 --> 36:01.550
back, and you want
to kick me out right away?

36:01.550 --> 36:03.400
I'm telling you, no way!

36:03.400 --> 36:05.110
You're taking this meat today,

36:05.110 --> 36:07.070
whether you like it or not!

36:07.710 --> 36:09.630
Qianqian, this Guo is

36:09.660 --> 36:10.960
selling water-injected meat.

36:10.960 --> 36:12.320
He even added borax.

36:12.320 --> 36:14.030
It looks fresh but tastes rotten.

36:14.030 --> 36:14.440
Stop shouting!

36:14.440 --> 36:16.030
He's notorious in our trade.

36:16.030 --> 36:17.070
Get lost! Get out of here!

36:17.070 --> 36:20.960
If you don't come out,
I'll spill the beans.

36:21.920 --> 36:24.110
This Chef Li is

36:24.110 --> 36:28.150
having an affair with Fan Changyu!

36:28.190 --> 36:28.970
What...

36:29.030 --> 36:30.030
Are you crazy?

36:30.030 --> 36:31.440
How dare he slander me!

36:31.840 --> 36:34.800
-My father scolded him a lot when he was alive.
-You're so old...

36:34.800 --> 36:35.550
I'll go teach him a lesson for you.

36:35.550 --> 36:36.960
-Shame on you!
-Changyu.

36:36.960 --> 36:38.110
What should I say about you?

36:38.110 --> 36:39.630
-Calm down.
-Should I say you're still potent,

36:39.630 --> 36:42.360
-or you're still going strong?
-It's my turf.

36:42.390 --> 36:44.350
-I got this.
-You're shameless!

36:46.070 --> 36:47.700
Manager Yu!

36:47.840 --> 36:49.360
If you don't come out now,

36:49.440 --> 36:51.970
I'll spill more secrets!

36:51.990 --> 36:53.790
-What's all the fuss?
-Get down!

36:55.480 --> 36:56.150
Manager.

36:56.550 --> 36:58.030
It's you, Butcher Guo.

36:58.630 --> 37:00.360
We're open for business.

37:00.360 --> 37:01.230
With you making such a scene,

37:01.230 --> 37:03.230
how am I supposed to run my business?

37:03.960 --> 37:06.150
Manager Yu, you finally came out.

37:08.670 --> 37:10.570
It's a small world for enemies.

37:12.360 --> 37:13.650
Manager Yu,

37:13.920 --> 37:15.920
your people are

37:16.280 --> 37:19.150
only doing these sneaky,

37:19.150 --> 37:21.800
dirty, shameless things.

37:21.800 --> 37:22.440
Are you going to handle it?

37:22.440 --> 37:24.100
Still talking nonsense here!

37:24.630 --> 37:27.100
Butcher Guo, you make it sound so real.

37:27.240 --> 37:29.800
Did you hide under the bed
and see it yourself?

37:29.800 --> 37:30.760
Did you see it?

37:33.360 --> 37:35.320
I suggest you, Manager Yu,

37:35.320 --> 37:37.270
give me an explanation today.

37:37.670 --> 37:39.760
Advisor Guo is

37:41.150 --> 37:43.040
my uncle.

37:44.190 --> 37:47.450
If I report this to my uncle,

37:47.630 --> 37:48.590
Manager Yu,

37:48.590 --> 37:51.510
you'll be in deep trouble.

37:52.910 --> 37:54.200
What a coincidence.

37:54.630 --> 37:57.670
Advisor Guo is drinking tea
in the private room in the back right now.

37:57.670 --> 37:59.550
Why don't we go ask him to judge?

38:02.670 --> 38:03.550
Really?

38:04.230 --> 38:06.550
Alright, let's go then.

38:09.870 --> 38:11.550
Take the meat.

38:14.210 --> 38:16.460
Guys, throw the meat out immediately.

38:17.210 --> 38:18.930
It's fine now. It's fine.

38:18.950 --> 38:20.200
Music, please.

38:20.440 --> 38:22.940
There will be singing
and dancing for the vibe soon.

38:22.940 --> 38:23.980
Everyone, relax.

38:24.010 --> 38:25.540
Enjoy your food and drinks.

38:31.780 --> 38:32.490
This way.

38:37.900 --> 38:38.490
Please.

38:42.800 --> 38:45.050
Uncle? Are you inside?

38:45.310 --> 38:46.750
Screw you inside!

38:48.070 --> 38:48.630
On my turf,

38:48.630 --> 38:50.430
how dare you, a nobody, run wild?

38:50.510 --> 38:52.350
I'm going to tear you apart today!

38:52.350 --> 38:53.370
Manager,

38:53.510 --> 38:54.880
your mink coat is expensive.

38:54.880 --> 38:56.480
Maybe let's stay out of this?

38:56.590 --> 38:57.230
Right.

38:57.230 --> 38:58.480
I almost forgot.

39:03.230 --> 39:05.110
Changyu, did that scare you?

39:06.880 --> 39:08.140
Just rough him up a bit.

39:08.190 --> 39:09.150
Don't kill him.

39:09.150 --> 39:09.840
Got it.

39:10.150 --> 39:11.920
Let's go.
There's nothing interesting to see here.

39:11.920 --> 39:13.920
Not as exciting as butchering pigs.

39:16.400 --> 39:17.160
Beat him up!

39:19.070 --> 39:20.190
Not the face!

39:20.190 --> 39:21.360
You know what?

39:21.360 --> 39:22.440
We have a show up ahead.

39:22.440 --> 39:23.230
It's amazing.

39:23.230 --> 39:25.230
Come on, I'll take you to have a look.

40:04.740 --> 40:05.940
My Lord, please look.

40:06.170 --> 40:08.370
It's that young lady from the other day.

40:08.900 --> 40:10.900
Well, just the one who lost her shoe.

40:11.030 --> 40:12.180
Her name is Fan Changyu.

40:12.180 --> 40:15.390
We searched everywhere,
yet it turns out that we had already met.

40:15.390 --> 40:16.610
Fan Changyu.

40:19.880 --> 40:21.580
Tell the spies in Lin'an
to keep a close watch.

40:21.580 --> 40:23.110
And those Suicide Warriors, too.

40:23.110 --> 40:24.740
Don't alert the magistrate yet.

40:24.740 --> 40:26.740
I want to meet the coroner in person.

40:26.830 --> 40:27.560
Understood.

40:38.400 --> 40:39.500
Changyu, you're back.

40:39.500 --> 40:40.340
Yeah, hello.

40:42.880 --> 40:43.610
Changyu.

40:47.360 --> 40:48.590
I'm back!

40:49.590 --> 40:50.480
Changyu.

40:51.070 --> 40:51.670
Come on.

40:54.340 --> 40:54.960
Look.

40:55.970 --> 40:58.240
Are these all for Changning?

40:58.320 --> 41:00.070
For Changning and Zheng.

41:00.280 --> 41:01.400
Zheng hates bitter medicine.

41:01.400 --> 41:02.800
So do you.

41:03.840 --> 41:04.570
You're back.

41:04.770 --> 41:05.440
Mrs. Zhao.

41:05.440 --> 41:07.240
You bought so much. What is this?

41:07.890 --> 41:10.300
So much candy! Is it New Year's Eve?

41:10.710 --> 41:12.360
I went to the Yixiang Restaurant
for a deal.

41:12.360 --> 41:13.760
Yu Qianqian gave it to me.

41:13.870 --> 41:15.220
That Manager Yu?

41:16.170 --> 41:18.520
I didn't expect her to be so nice.

41:19.670 --> 41:20.670
A woman running

41:20.670 --> 41:23.030
2 restaurants
in both the county and Lin'an.

41:23.030 --> 41:24.030
Very impressive.

41:24.190 --> 41:25.320
You know her, too?

41:25.440 --> 41:26.550
Of course.

41:27.070 --> 41:29.200
She came to Lin'an pregnant back then,

41:30.030 --> 41:31.070
with no relatives to turn to.

41:31.070 --> 41:32.800
She was even worse off than you.

41:32.920 --> 41:34.120
Where is her husband?

41:34.670 --> 41:35.800
I don't know.

41:35.800 --> 41:37.190
He must be capable.

41:37.190 --> 41:38.230
Otherwise, how could he marry

41:38.230 --> 41:39.590
such a capable woman?

41:59.030 --> 42:00.730
Changning is sleeping here in my place.

42:00.730 --> 42:02.730
Why don't you go back to hit the sack?

42:04.360 --> 42:06.560
I'll roast the persimmons a bit longer.

42:06.630 --> 42:08.420
The persimmon tree isn't falling.

42:08.420 --> 42:11.020
You can roast persimmons
anytime in your life.

42:11.320 --> 42:14.780
But are you going to avoid
consummating the marriage forever?

42:20.140 --> 42:22.270
Mrs. Zhao, Yan Zheng and I actually...

42:23.670 --> 42:24.480
Didn't you say Yan Zheng

42:24.480 --> 42:26.030
agreed to leave with you?

42:26.670 --> 42:29.230
He said he would leave with me for now.

42:30.030 --> 42:31.070
But what about the future?

42:31.070 --> 42:32.600
Why worry about the future?

42:33.510 --> 42:34.360
Since he married into your family,

42:34.360 --> 42:36.120
you have to take the initiative.

42:36.120 --> 42:38.010
No matter what's on your mind,

42:38.580 --> 42:41.300
I think Yan Zheng is
a wonderful young man.

42:41.630 --> 42:44.090
Look at the huge trouble
your family ran into this time.

42:44.090 --> 42:47.010
He went to save Changning
despite all his injuries.

42:47.070 --> 42:47.630
Also,

42:48.150 --> 42:49.230
at the county government office court,

42:49.230 --> 42:51.150
if Mr. Sun hadn't arrived in time,

42:51.340 --> 42:54.540
he really would have
gone all out to fight the magistrate.

42:56.710 --> 42:58.550
With such a responsible man,

42:58.630 --> 43:00.510
why don't you seize the opportunity

43:00.510 --> 43:02.000
to get things fully done?

43:02.320 --> 43:03.590
Once you sleep together,

43:03.590 --> 43:05.070
his heart will be with you.

43:06.920 --> 43:09.630
If I just go consummate the marriage
with him for no reason,

43:09.630 --> 43:10.880
what would that make me?

43:10.880 --> 43:13.150
He's your husband. What's wrong with that?

43:13.150 --> 43:15.350
Do you need to pick a lucky date for that?

43:15.590 --> 43:16.510
Mrs. Zhao.

43:17.960 --> 43:19.000
Fine.

43:19.710 --> 43:21.370
Let me give you another trick.

43:22.670 --> 43:25.090
During the day, I washed the bedding

43:25.550 --> 43:27.480
you used on the floor in your house.

43:28.980 --> 43:32.110
He won't bear to see you
sleep on the bare floor, would he?

44:02.430 --> 44:03.330
Come here.
